* Her eyes were empty when they turned and looked at Prowl, nothing left in 
them. All tey said was that she was fithting because she had to or die, and 
that was all that she was living for now.*

" You don't care what I have to say or think, you all went ahead and did all 
this without me and you're going on to do it without me.
A AM the commander here, I thought I counted. I was wrong."

* She hated him, hated them all but she knew that was a wrong feeling and 
she tried to fight it.  But she knew that she was no commander, and she had 
thought it cool at the time...but now she wished she would have never landed 
on this planet.
She just wanted it all to stop.
Everything.
IR took in a breath, she had to calm down.*

" Just build the slagging thing and get out of my sight."

* Her expression then changed, from miserable to angered.*
